modShortDescription: A quick dirt bike. Only one seat. Same storage as bicycle. Unlocks with Grease Monkey 3. Decent fuel mileage, but low capacity.
modDescription:
A quick dirt [bike](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-bike/). And no neighbors to complain about it!

Only one seat. Same storage as a bicycle.

Unlocks with Grease Monkey 3\. Decent fuel mileage, but low capacity.

## Changelog

* **_(new)_** Updated for A20.
* Added new engine/horn sounds.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/bdubyah/Mods---A20/-/archive/main/Mods---A20-main.zip?path=Dirt%20Bike)** for A20  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A19/tree/master/Dirt%20Bike)** for A19
